# Requirement addressed: Code Review Governance
# Location: Technical Specification/System Design/Development & Deployment

# Default owners for everything in the repo
# These owners will be requested for review on all PRs
*                       @team-lead @repo-admin

# Backend team owns all files under src/backend/
src/backend/**          @backend-team

# Frontend team owns all files under src/web/
src/web/**             @frontend-team

# DevOps team owns all infrastructure files
infrastructure/**      @devops-team

# CI/CD team owns all GitHub workflow files
.github/workflows/**   @ci-cd-team